description:
Have you ever thought about giving a talk? Now is your chance to start small. We are looking for 5-6 speakers to give quick (10-15 minute) talks. If you would like to be considered, please reach out to us. Please submit your talks for consideration to this form: https://forms.gle/VW3A4gLptkoA3Hep6

Date subject to change.
Speakers and Topics coming soon.
title: Virtual - Lightning Talks
